text.tspan: For A Discussion on Gender in Video Games, From the French Revolution to
#gamergate, please attend UCLA’s Center for the Study of Women’s
Conference, with Special Panel “Gamers ‘n’ Geeks: Gendered
Roles and Professionalism in the Gaming Industry,”
